Usage: analyze_signal_resistance [-help] [-instance_pair_list_file <string>]
                                 -net <string> [-output_dir <string>]
                                 [-report <string>] [-threshold <float>]

-help                                 # Prints out the command usage
-instance_pair_list_file <string>     # signal net instance-pin pairs for which
                                      # reffective need to be computed
                                      # (string, optional)
-net <string>                         # <name of signal net> (string, required)
-output_dir <string>                  # output directory (string, optional)
-report <string>                      # output file for Effective R
                                      # (string, optional)
-threshold <float>                    # threshold R value in ohm
                                      # (float, optional)